{"tid":2338882,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"為應付非法集結，警方葵涌已設路障，機動部隊現場戒備！","createTime":"2020-12-24T09:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T12:32:21.000Z","uid":219007,"like":27,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"ce66060e026990fccfb1254fc7b6ffeaf0869252","tid":2338882,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:31:15.000Z","msg":"【警稱足夠警力應付非法集結　未入黑葵涌「吹波波」　藍帽子同戒備】<br />\n<br />\n網上有號召網民在平安夜紀念 12 港人活動，警方已發佈消息指會部署足夠警力應付可能出<br />\n現的非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n下午約四時許，警方已在葵涌迴旋處附近設路障，由九龍交通部警員作酒精呼氣測試；但讀者指附近停泊了一部警察小巴，車上有機動部隊警員。<br />\n<br />\n而查車時，有青年人被要求下車站在公路旁，警察亦罕見地在公路上擺設桌椅工作。<br />\n<br />\n(照片由讀者提供)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3754996564585936/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3754996564585936%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76Mcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=45fc6f1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3754996564585936/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"7b77b25ec51817a3b86587c607dba47214ab2eee","tid":2338882,"uid":219007,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:32:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0xDR0yU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0xDR0yU.jpg&h=241dbdfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2027c4372cc8423a5ed8c11cb03cfb73222a8b63","tid":2338882,"uid":10905,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"呀蛇快d出動啦<br />\n我sp話佢老公仲係局入面等緊出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97469bcf121a32f3f5904a5d51e38979a18dabc","tid":2338882,"uid":42188,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:34:31.000Z","msg":"班popo無女仲要平安夜開ot<br />\n心理唔平衡到玩封路阻人返去同囡囡扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/